description: Rare double unit on the 41st floor of Harbor Point! This expansive condo offers sweeping panoramic views of Millennium Park and the Chicago skyline through floor to ceiling windows. With a flexible open layout and generous square footage, the home is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living.  In addition to 3 bdr/2bath, there is a den, laundry room and extra storage. Multiple living areas, dining spaces, and private retreats give you the freedom to create the lifestyle you envision. Enjoy full building amenities including 24-hour door staff, indoor pool, fitness center, spa, sundeck, and onsite market just steps from the lakefront, Maggie Daley Park, and the best of downtown Chicago.
